userdoc.notice: Educational Simple AMM that supports adding/removing liquidity and swapping between two ERC20 tokens.

devdoc.details: Educational: not audited. Do NOT use as-is in production.

params.amountIn: amount of fromToken sent (user must approve first)
params.fromToken: the token the user sends in (must be token0 or token1)
params.toToken: the token the user wants out
